  "description": "A stunning panoramic view of the Golden Gate Bridge shrouded in a dense, orange fog. The bridge is silhouetted against a brilliant, almost blinding, orange sun that dominates the upper portion of the frame. The sun appears as a glowing orb, partially obscured by the fog, creating a dramatic and ethereal effect. The water below reflects the orange hue, creating a seamless blend between sky and sea. In the distance, hints of land and other bridge structures are visible, though blurred by the fog. The overall impression is one of mystery and grandeur, evoking a sense of awe and tranquility.",
